<span id="freeTextContainer10717141589297607179">Reading this was slow torture. I made it to page 37 before I couldn&apos;t take anymore. If I was still in college and forced to read it for class I would finish. But, thank goodness, my college days are long behind me and I don&apos;t have to play by those rules. </span>
